msgid "Functionals"
msgstr "Funcionals"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:13
msgid ""
"The :mod:`~qilisdk.functionals` module provides high-level quantum "
"execution procedures by combining tools from the :mod:`~qilisdk.analog`, "
":mod:`~qilisdk.digital`, and :mod:`~qilisdk.core` modules. Currently, it "
"includes the following execution functionals:"
msgstr ""
"El mòdul :mod:`~qilisdk.functionals` proporciona procediments d'execució "
"quàntica d'alt nivell combinant eines dels mòduls :mod:`~qilisdk.analog`, "
":mod:`~qilisdk.digital` i :mod:`~qilisdk.core`. Actualment, inclou els "
"següents funcionals d'execució:"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:16
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation`: "
"Propagates a digital quantum circuit through the backend."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation`: "
"Propaga un circuit quàntic digital a través del backend."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:17
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution`: Simulates"
" analog time evolution of one or more Hamiltonians according to a time-"
"dependent schedule."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution`: Simula "
"l'evolució temporal analògica d'un o més Hamiltonians d'acord amb un esquema "
"dependent del temps."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:18
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.QuantumReservoir`: Runs a"
" quantum reservoir pipeline (pre-processing, reservoir dynamics, post-"
"processing) across multiple input layers."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.QuantumReservoir`: Executa "
"una cadena de reservori quàntic (pre-processament, dinàmica del reservori, "
"post-processament) a través de múltiples capes d'entrada."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:20
msgid ""
"Moreover, it provides more complex functionals that are used to execute "
"more complex algorithms:"
msgstr ""
"A més, proporciona funcionals més complexos que s'utilitzen per executar "
"algorismes més complexos:"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:22
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program.VariationalProgram`: "
"Builds parameterized program to be optimized in a hybrid quantum-"
"classical environment."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program.VariationalProgram`: "
"Construeix un programa parametritzat per ser optimitzat en un entorn "
"quàntic-clàssic híbrid."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:25
msgid "Architecture Overview"
msgstr "Visió General de l'Arquitectura"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:27
msgid ""
"Every functional conforms to the abstract "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.Functional` interface. Primitive "
"functionals such as "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation` and "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution` also "
"inherit from "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.PrimitiveFunctional`, which mixes"
" in the :class:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable` contract. "
"This lets backends query and update symbolic parameters consistently "
"before execution."
msgstr ""
"Cada funcional s'ajusta a la interfície abstracta "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.Functional`. Els funcionals "
"primitius com ara "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation` i "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution` també "
"hereten de "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.PrimitiveFunctional`, que incorpora "
"el contracte :class:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable`. "
"Això permet que els backends consultin i actualitzin paràmetres simbòlics de "
"manera coherent abans de l'execució."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:34
msgid ""
"Readout is decoupled from functionals: measurement details (shots, "
"observables, state tomography) are specified via :mod:`~qilisdk.readout` "
"objects passed to the backend's "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute` method. All primitive "
"functionals return a unified "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`."
msgstr ""
"La lectura està desacoblada dels funcionals: els detalls de la mesura (shots, "
"observables, tomografia d'estat) s'especifiquen mitjançant objectes "
":mod:`~qilisdk.readout` passats al mètode "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute` del backend. Tots els "
"funcionals primitius retornen un "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` unificat."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:39
msgid "Result Objects"
msgstr "Objectes de Resultat"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:41
msgid ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`"
msgstr ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:42
msgid ""
"The unified result type for all primitive functionals. Access results "
"through: ``samples`` for shot counts, ``probabilities`` for measurement "
"probabilities, ``state`` for the terminal "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` state (when using "
":meth:`~qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_state_tomography`), and"
" ``expectation_values`` for expectation values (when using "
":meth:`~qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_expectation`). When "
"``store_intermediate_results=True``, intermediate results are available "
"via ``intermediate_states``, ``intermediate_samples``, "
"``intermediate_probabilities``, and ``intermediate_expectation_values``."
msgstr ""
"El tipus de resultat unificat per a tots els funcionals primitius. Accediu "
"als resultats mitjançant: ``samples`` per als comptadors de shots, "
"``probabilities`` per a les probabilitats de mesura, ``state`` per a l'estat "
"final :class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` (quan s'utilitza "
":meth:`~qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_state_tomography`), i "
"``expectation_values`` per als valors esperats (quan s'utilitza "
":meth:`~qilisdk.readout.readout_spec.Readout.with_expectation`). Quan "
"``store_intermediate_results=True``, els resultats intermedis estan disponibles "
"mitjançant ``intermediate_states``, ``intermediate_samples``, "
"``intermediate_probabilities`` i ``intermediate_expectation_values``."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:49
msgid ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program_result.VariationalProgramResult`"
msgstr ":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program_result.VariationalProgramResult`"

