#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:136
msgid "Analog Evolution"
msgstr "Evolució Analògica"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:138
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution` "
"functional simulates analog evolution of a quantum system under one or "
"more Hamiltonians, following a specified time-dependent schedule. Its "
"parameter interface mirrors that of "
":class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`, making it straightforward to "
"sweep control waveforms or pulse amplitudes from classical optimizers."
msgstr ""
"El funcional :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution` "
"simula l'evolució analògica d'un sistema quàntic sota un o més Hamiltonians, "
"seguint un esquema especificat dependent del temps. La seva interfície de "
"paràmetres reflecteix la de :class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`, el "
"que facilita escanejar formes d'ona de control o amplituds de pols des "
"d'optimitzadors clàssics."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:142
msgid ""
"Observables and shot counts are specified separately via readout objects "
"passed to :meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute`."
msgstr ""
"Els observables i els comptadors de shots s'especifiquen separadament "
"mitjançant objectes de lectura passats a "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute`."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:147
msgid ""
"**schedule** (:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`): Defines total "
"evolution time, time steps, Hamiltonians, and their time-dependent "
"coefficients."
msgstr ""
"**schedule** (:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`): Defineix el temps "
"total d'evolució, els passos de temps, els Hamiltonians i els seus "
"coeficients dependents del temps."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:148
msgid ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Initial state"
" of the system."
msgstr ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Estat inicial "
"del sistema."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:149
msgid ""
"**store_intermediate_results** (bool, optional): If True, records the "
"state at each time step. Default is False."
msgstr ""
"**store_intermediate_results** (bool, opcional): Si és True, registra l'estat "
"a cada pas de temps. El valor per defecte és False."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:153
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: Inspect"
" :attr:`expectation_values` for measured observables, :attr:`state` for "
"the closing state, and :attr:`intermediate_states` and "
":attr:`intermediate_expectation_values` when "
"``store_intermediate_results`` is enabled."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: "
"Inspeccioneu :attr:`expectation_values` per als observables mesurats, "
":attr:`state` per a l'estat final, i :attr:`intermediate_states` i "
":attr:`intermediate_expectation_values` quan "
"``store_intermediate_results`` està activat."

