#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:225
msgid "Quantum Reservoirs"
msgstr "Reservoris Quàntics"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:227
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.QuantumReservoir` "
"functional executes a reservoir pipeline over a sequence of inputs. Each "
"layer applies an optional pre-processing circuit, an analog reservoir "
"dynamics block (:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`), and an "
"optional post-processing circuit, followed by measurements of one or more"
" observables. The optional ``qubits_to_reset`` list can be used to reset "
"selected qubits between layers."
msgstr ""
"El funcional "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.QuantumReservoir` executa "
"una cadena de reservori sobre una seqüència d'entrades. Cada capa aplica un "
"circuit de pre-processament opcional, un bloc de dinàmica del reservori "
"analògic (:class:`~qilisdk.analog.schedule.Schedule`), i un circuit de "
"post-processament opcional, seguit de mesures d'un o més observables. La "
"llista opcional ``qubits_to_reset`` es pot utilitzar per restablir qubits "
"seleccionats entre capes."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:232
msgid ""
"The reservoir inputs are represented using "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput` "
"parameters. These behave like standard "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Parameter` objects but are marked as non-"
"trainable so they can be driven by input data sequences rather than "
"optimization loops."
msgstr ""
"Les entrades del reservori es representen mitjançant paràmetres "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput`. Aquests es "
"comporten com objectes :class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Parameter` estàndard "
"però estan marcats com a no entrenables perquè puguin ser dirigits per "
"seqüències de dades d'entrada en lloc de bucles d'optimització."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:238
msgid ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Initial state"
" of the reservoir."
msgstr ""
"**initial_state** (:class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor`): Estat inicial "
"del reservori."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:239
msgid ""
"**reservoir_layer** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirLayer`): "
"Defines pre/post-processing, reservoir dynamics, observables, and reset "
"policy."
msgstr ""
"**reservoir_layer** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirLayer`): "
"Defineix el pre/post-processament, la dinàmica del reservori, els observables "
"i la política de restabliment."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:241
msgid ""
"**input_per_layer** (List[Dict[str, float]]): Input values to apply at "
"each layer, keyed by input parameter names (typically the labels of "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput`)."
msgstr ""
"**input_per_layer** (List[Dict[str, float]]): Valors d'entrada a aplicar a "
"cada capa, indexats pels noms dels paràmetres d'entrada (típicament les "
"etiquetes de "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput`)."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:246
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: Access "
"per-layer expectation values via :attr:`expectation_values`, plus "
"optional states via :attr:`state`."
msgstr ""
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult`: Accediu "
"als valors esperats per capa mitjançant :attr:`expectation_values`, més els "
"estats opcionals mitjançant :attr:`state`."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:292
msgid "Encoding Input Data"
msgstr "Codificació de Dades d'Entrada"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:294
msgid ""
"You can inject classical data into a reservoir layer in multiple places. "
"The only requirement is that the keys in ``input_per_layer`` match the "
"labels of the "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput` objects "
"you place in the layer."
msgstr ""
"Podeu injectar dades clàssiques en una capa de reservori en múltiples llocs. "
"L'únic requisit és que les claus a ``input_per_layer`` coincideixin amb les "
"etiquetes dels objectes "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.quantum_reservoirs.ReservoirInput` que "
"col·loqueu a la capa."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:298
msgid "**1. Encode with input and output circuits**"
msgstr "**1. Codificar amb circuits d'entrada i sortida**"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:335
msgid "**2. Encode directly in Hamiltonian parameters**"
msgstr "**2. Codificar directament en paràmetres del Hamiltonià**"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:366
msgid "**3. Encode in the schedule profile and duration**"
msgstr "**3. Codificar en el perfil de l'esquema i la durada**"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:404
msgid "Variational Programs"
msgstr "Programes Variacionals"

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:406
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program.VariationalProgram` "
"functional gathers the pieces required for a variational quantum "
"algorithm. It accepts a parameterized primitive functional, an optimizer,"
" and a cost function. When you call "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute` it evaluates the "
"functional repeatedly with updated parameters, feeds the resulting "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` into the"
" supplied cost function, and finally returns a "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program_result.VariationalProgramResult`."
" Parameter constraints (inequalities/equalities on parameters) are "
"attached at this level via the ``parameter_constraints`` argument; this "
"is the place to enforce relations like ``theta >= phi`` or cross-"
"parameter bounds across all QiliSDK functionals. Only parameters marked "
"as trainable are optimized during this loop."
msgstr ""
"El funcional "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program.VariationalProgram` "
"reuneix les peces necessàries per a un algorisme quàntic variacional. Accepta "
"un funcional primitiu parametritzat, un optimitzador i una funció de cost. "
"Quan es crida "
":meth:`~qilisdk.backends.backend.Backend.execute`, avalua el funcional "
"repetidament amb paràmetres actualitzats, introdueix el "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional_result.FunctionalResult` resultant "
"a la funció de cost subministrada, i finalment retorna un "
":class:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program_result.VariationalProgramResult`."
" Les restriccions de paràmetres (desigualtats/igualtats sobre paràmetres) "
"s'adjunten a aquest nivell mitjançant l'argument ``parameter_constraints``; "
"aquest és el lloc per imposar relacions com ``theta >= phi`` o límits "
"creuats entre paràmetres en tots els funcionals de QiliSDK. Només els "
"paràmetres marcats com a entrenables s'optimitzen durant aquest bucle."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:418
msgid ""
"**functional** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.PrimitiveFunctional`): "
"Parameterized primitive to optimize (for instance "
":class:`DigitalPropagation "
"<qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation>` or "
":class:`AnalogEvolution "
"<qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution>`)."
msgstr ""
"**functional** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.functionals.functional.PrimitiveFunctional`): "
"Primitiu parametritzat a optimitzar (per exemple "
":class:`DigitalPropagation "
"<qilisdk.functionals.digital_propagation.DigitalPropagation>` o "
":class:`AnalogEvolution "
"<qilisdk.functionals.analog_evolution.AnalogEvolution>`)."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:421
msgid ""
"**optimizer** (:class:`~qilisdk.optimizers.optimizer.Optimizer`): "
"Classical optimizer that proposes new parameter values and optionally "
"stores intermediate iterates."
msgstr ""
"**optimizer** (:class:`~qilisdk.optimizers.optimizer.Optimizer`): "
"Optimitzador clàssic que proposa nous valors de paràmetres i opcionalment "
"emmagatzema els iterats intermedis."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:423
msgid ""
"**cost_function** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction`): Object "
"that maps the functional results to a scalar cost; frequently constructed"
" from a :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model`."
msgstr ""
"**cost_function** "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.cost_function.CostFunction`): Objecte que "
"associa els resultats del funcional a un cost escalar; freqüentment construït "
"a partir d'un :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model`."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:425
msgid ""
"**store_intermediate_results** (bool, optional): When True, the optimizer"
" keeps the intermediate steps, which are exposed through "
":attr:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program_result.VariationalProgramResult.intermediate_results`."
msgstr ""
"**store_intermediate_results** (bool, opcional): Quan és True, l'optimitzador "
"conserva els passos intermedis, que s'exposen mitjançant "
":attr:`~qilisdk.functionals.variational_program_result.VariationalProgramResult.intermediate_results`."

#: ../../modules/functionals/functionals.rst:427
msgid ""
"**parameter_constraints** "
"(list[:class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.ComparisonTerm`], optional): "
"Constraints on functional parameters (e.g., ``theta >= 0.5``) evaluated "
"before each optimizer update. This is the supported entry point for "
"enforcing parameter relations in QiliSDK."
msgstr ""
"**parameter_constraints** "
